section.def:
driver
                (駕駛人), in relation to any vehicle, means any
            person who is in charge of or assisting in the control of it;

operator
                (營運者) means a person who has entered into a
            management agreement with the Government;

register
                (登記冊) has the same meaning as in the Road Traffic
            Ordinance (Cap. 374);

registered
                (登記) means registered under the Road Traffic
            Ordinance (Cap. 374);

toll
                (使用費) means a charge specified in a regulation
            made under section 27 for the use of the Lantau Link;

paragraph.content:
for the purpose of collecting any toll, fee or charge or requiring payment
                    of such toll, fee or charge where the driver of a vehicle has evaded payment of
                    that toll, fee or charge;

enter, examine and search a vehicle and any thing therein or thereon if the
                    authorized officer reasonably suspects that that vehicle is carrying dangerous
                    goods;

the licence is not displayed on an electronic device through an electronic
                    platform specified under section 110A(1)(c) of the Road Traffic
                    Ordinance (Cap. 374);

the licence cannot be read or scanned by the authorized officer because of
                    a defect of the electronic device on which the licence is purportedly displayed;
                    or

has committed a hawker offence within the meaning of section 83
                    of
                    the Public Health and Municipal Services Ordinance (Cap. 132);

the imposition and collection of additional charges (including surcharges)
                    in respect of any evasion or underpayment of tolls payable for the use of the
                    Lantau Link;

the imposition and collection of administration fees in respect of any
                    refund of any overpayment of tolls made in cash for the use of the Lantau
                    Link;

the imposition and collection of fees in respect of the processing of an
                    application, or the processing of an application and issue of a permit by the
                    Commissioner or an operator with the approval of the Commissioner;
